The paper discusses the efficacy of the BFLOAT16 format for deep learning training across various domains such as image classification, speech recognition, language modeling, generative networks, and industrial recommendation systems. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
